# CV Builder - Complete Sections & Fields Structure

## üìã Top 10 Most Vital CV Sections

---

## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Personal Information
**Purpose**: Core identity and contact details  
**Display Priority**: Header (Top of CV)  
**Required**: Yes

### Fields:

| Field Name | Type | Required | Validation | Example |
|------------|------|----------|------------|---------|
| `firstName` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-50 chars | John |
| `lastName` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-50 chars | Doe |
| `email` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | Valid email | john.doe@email.com |
| `phone` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | International format | +1-234-567-8900 |
| `profilePhoto` | File/URL | ‚ùå No | Image (2MB max) | /uploads/photo.jpg |
| `title` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | Professional title | Senior Software Engineer |
| `address` | Object | ‚ùå No | - | See below |
| `city` | String | ‚ùå No | 2-100 chars | San Francisco |
| `state` | String | ‚ùå No | 2-100 chars | California |
| `country` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | United States |
| `zipCode` | String | ‚ùå No | Postal code | 94102 |
| `dateOfBirth` | Date | ‚ùå No | Valid date | 1990-05-15 |
| `nationality` | String | ‚ùå No | 2-100 chars | American |
| `linkedIn` | String | ‚ùå No | Valid URL | linkedin.com/in/johndoe |
| `portfolio` | String | ‚ùå No | Valid URL | johndoe.com |
| `github` | String | ‚ùå No | Valid URL | github.com/johndoe |
| `twitter` | String | ‚ùå No | Valid URL | twitter.com/johndoe |
| `website` | String | ‚ùå No | Valid URL | mywebsite.com |

---

## 2Ô∏è‚É£ Professional Summary / Objective
**Purpose**: Elevator pitch - who you are professionally  
**Display Priority**: Below personal info  
**Required**: Recommended

### Fields:

| Field Name | Type | Required | Validation | Example |
|------------|------|----------|------------|---------|
| `summaryType` | Enum | ‚úÖ Yes | 'summary' \| 'objective' | summary |
| `content` | Text | ‚úÖ Yes | 50-500 chars | Results-driven software engineer with 5+ years... |
| `aiGenerated` | Boolean | ‚ùå No | true/false | false |
| `keywords` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['leadership', 'agile', 'python'] |

---

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Work Experience
**Purpose**: Employment history and achievements  
**Display Priority**: After summary  
**Required**: Yes (at least 1 entry)

### Fields per Entry:

| Field Name | Type | Required | Validation | Example |
|------------|------|----------|------------|---------|
| `jobTitle` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | Senior Software Engineer |
| `company` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | Tech Corp Inc. |
| `location` | String | ‚ùå No | City, Country | San Francisco, USA |
| `employmentType` | Enum | ‚ùå No | full-time, part-time, contract, freelance, internship | full-time |
| `startDate` | Date | ‚úÖ Yes | Valid date | 2020-01-15 |
| `endDate` | Date | ‚ùå No | Valid date or null | 2023-05-30 |
| `isCurrent` | Boolean | ‚úÖ Yes | true/false | false |
| `description` | Text | ‚ùå No | Max 2000 chars | Led a team of 5 developers... |
| `achievements` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['Increased performance by 40%', 'Led migration to cloud'] |
| `responsibilities` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['Code reviews', 'Architecture design'] |
| `technologies` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['React', 'Node.js', 'AWS'] |
| `order` | Number | ‚úÖ Yes | Integer | 1 |
| `aiGenerated` | Boolean | ‚ùå No | true/false | false |

---

## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Education
**Purpose**: Academic background and qualifications  
**Display Priority**: After work experience  
**Required**: Yes (at least 1 entry)

### Fields per Entry:

| Field Name | Type | Required | Validation | Example |
|------------|------|----------|------------|---------|
| `institution` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-200 chars | Stanford University |
| `degree` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | Bachelor of Science |
| `fieldOfStudy` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | Computer Science |
| `location` | String | ‚ùå No | City, Country | Stanford, CA, USA |
| `startDate` | Date | ‚úÖ Yes | Valid date | 2012-09-01 |
| `endDate` | Date | ‚ùå No | Valid date or null | 2016-06-15 |
| `isOngoing` | Boolean | ‚úÖ Yes | true/false | false |
| `gpa` | Number | ‚ùå No | 0.0-4.0 or 0-100 | 3.8 |
| `gpaScale` | Enum | ‚ùå No | '4.0' \| '5.0' \| '100' | 4.0 |
| `honors` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['Magna Cum Laude', 'Dean\'s List'] |
| `relevantCoursework` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['Data Structures', 'Machine Learning'] |
| `activities` | Text | ‚ùå No | Max 500 chars | President of Computer Science Club |
| `thesis` | String | ‚ùå No | Max 200 chars | Deep Learning for Image Recognition |
| `order` | Number | ‚úÖ Yes | Integer | 1 |

