## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Skills
**Purpose**: Technical and soft skills with proficiency levels  
**Display Priority**: Sidebar or after experience  
**Required**: Yes (at least 3 skills)

### Fields per Entry:

| Field Name | Type | Required | Validation | Example |
|------------|------|----------|------------|---------|
| `name` | String | ‚úÖ Yes | 2-100 chars | JavaScript |
| `category` | Enum | ‚úÖ Yes | technical, soft, language, tool, framework, other | technical |
| `proficiencyLevel` | Number | ‚úÖ Yes | 1-10 or enum | 8 |
| `proficiencyLabel` | Enum | ‚ùå No | beginner, intermediate, advanced, expert | advanced |
| `yearsOfExperience` | Number | ‚ùå No | 0-50 | 5 |
| `lastUsed` | Date | ‚ùå No | Valid date | 2023-10-01 |
| `certifications` | Array | ‚ùå No | String array | ['AWS Certified Developer'] |
| `endorsements` | Number | ‚ùå No | Integer | 45 |
| `order` | Number | ‚úÖ Yes | Integer | 1 |
| `isHighlighted` | Boolean | ‚ùå No | true/false | true |

### Skill Categories Detail:

**Technical Skills**: Programming languages, frameworks, databases
**Soft Skills**: Communication, Leadership, Problem-solving
**Language Skills**: English (Native), Spanish (Fluent)
**Tools**: Git, Docker, Jira, Figma
**Frameworks**: React, Angular, Django
**Other**: Domain-specific skills

